History
=======

0.1.1 (2018-02-10)
------------------

* fix rsync ``options`` arg behavior


0.1.0 (2018-02-10)
------------------

* added rsync handler


0.0.3 (2017-10-17)
------------------

* correctly handle clear_env in sphinx:sphinx_script
* update cryptography, tox, sphinx, wheel


0.0.1 (2017-09-10)
------------------

* First release on PyPI.


0.0.2.dev4 (2017-09-10)
-----------------------

* Fixed ignored excludes in lftp_sync


